#Pl√©nitude #ArnaudDonckele #3michelinstar 

Welcome to Paris. Home of the Mona Lisa, the Eiffel Tower and our restaurant for today - Pl√©nitude.
It opened in 2021 and was awarded 3 Michelin stars in it‚Äôs first year. The head chef is Arnaud Donckele. Crafting a menu that puts sauce in the spotlight is genius. In French cuisine, sauce plays a major role, but maybe not the attention it should. Chef Donckele gives it that attention. 
I can honestly say my experience at Plenitude was perfect.
